title: Samsung just teased its Oura Ring killer — the Galaxy Ring
description: Samsung is officially entering the smart ring arena, one where the likes of Oura have left a mark. The Galaxy ring looks sleek, but that's all we know for now.

title: Check out Wing’s largest delivery drone yet
description: Drone specialist Wing has announced plans to add a bigger drone to its delivery fleet that it says will simplify and streamline larger orders.
